{{dablink|本文講述的是中土大陸的武器，關於黑箭的其他意思詳見[[黑箭_(消歧義)|黑箭 (消歧義)]]}}

'''黑箭'''（Black Arrow）是[[托爾金|托爾金]]（J. R. R. Tolkien）奇幻小說裡的虛構武器。

黑箭是[[河谷鎮國王列表|河谷鎮國王]][[吉瑞安|吉瑞安]]（Girion）家族的傳家之寶，傳至神射手[[巴德_(中土大陸)|巴德]]（Bard）。當[[史矛革|史矛革]]（Smaug）襲擊[[長湖鎮_(哈比人歷險記)|長湖鎮]]時，這是巴德剩下的唯一一支箭矢，巴德以黑箭舉弓射入史矛革的左胸（史矛革的弱點），射殺了史矛革。黑箭可能是由山下國王[[索爾_(中土大陸)|索爾]]（Thrór）鑄造的。不知道黑箭是否具有魔力，但巴德說每次他使用黑箭後，總是能收回的（如[[貝賴格|貝賴格]]的[[戴賴爾|戴賴爾]]）。

==改編描述==
在《[[哈比人電影系列|哈比人電影系列]]》中，黑箭被描繪成一根很長的箭，需要使用長弓射出<ref>{{Cite news|url=http://www.theonering.net/torwp/2014/07/26/91359-analysis-bard-the-black-arrow-and-the-windlance/|title=Analysis: Bard, the Black Arrow and the Windlance|date=2014-07-26|newspaper=TheOneRing.net|accessdate=2018-05-05|language=en-US|archive-date=2021-03-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210303212517/https://www.theonering.net/torwp/2014/07/26/91359-analysis-bard-the-black-arrow-and-the-windlance/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=http://middleearthnews.com/2014/01/30/anti-smaug-double-crossbow-ballista-created-by-joerg-sprave/|title=Anti Smaug Double Crossbow Ballista Created By Joerg Sprave|accessdate=2018-05-05|date=2014-01-30|publisher=Middle-earth News|archive-date=2020-05-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200516235346/http://middleearthnews.com/2014/01/30/anti-smaug-double-crossbow-ballista-created-by-joerg-sprave/|dead-url=no}}</ref>，僅存的一根來自河谷鎮的黑箭一直藏於巴德家中<ref>{{Cite news|url=http://herocomplex.latimes.com/movies/hobbit-battle-of-the-five-armies-luke-evans-on-bard-battle/#/0|title=‘Hobbit: Battle of the Five Armies’: Luke Evans on Bard, battle|author=|date=2014-12-09|newspaper=Los Angeles Times|accessdate=2018-05-05|language=en-US|archive-date=2018-10-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181006004938/http://herocomplex.latimes.com/movies/hobbit-battle-of-the-five-armies-luke-evans-on-bard-battle/#/0|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.wired.com/2014/11/black-arrow-actually-kill-dragon/|title=Could the Black Arrow Actually Kill a Dragon?|newspaper=WIRED|accessdate=2018-05-05|language=en-US|archive-date=2021-04-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210411164421/https://www.wired.com/2014/11/black-arrow-actually-kill-dragon/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。巴德在被[[長湖鎮鎮長|長湖鎮鎮長]][[逮捕|逮捕]]前把黑箭託付給兒子[[貝恩_(中土大陸)|貝恩]]；後來當惡龍來襲之時，巴德在鐘樓上利用木頭建造了一個臨時弩弓，並以貝恩的肩膀當支撐點穩定黑箭，終射殺了史矛革<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://diymag.com/2015/12/17/the-10-best-battles-from-the-hobbit-extended-editions|title=The 10 Best Battles From The Hobbit: Extended Editions|accessdate=2018-05-05|date=2015-12-17|publisher=DIY|language=en|archive-date=2018-05-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180505204903/http://diymag.com/2015/12/17/the-10-best-battles-from-the-hobbit-extended-editions|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

